item.title: Cannot give my self owner
item.dc:creator: @DannyIsSoPro DannyIsSoPro
item.description:
@DannyIsSoPro wrote:

ston3:

I’ve tried giving myself admin on my server, but it insta-changes it to donator rank. I made a new account, and without anything it gives me donator rank on new acc. How do i fix this? It also shows that normal players are admins + Any help? PI

Maybe it’s an anti-leech.

But to make yourself owner or admin, go into the playerSaves and find your account, open it with notepad or notepad++. Find “rights” without the “”. If you see 0 within rights, change it to 2 or 3.

Anyways, look inside of player.java and see if theirs a method that…well…causes your problem lol. Btw player.java is just a guess to look at.

PS: Did you switch sources already?lol?
